title: Static Analysis

android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATIO.description: Access coarse location sources, such as the mobile network database, to determine an approximate phone location, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine approximately where you are.

android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION.description: Access fine location sources, such as the Global Positioning System on the phone, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine where you are and may consume additional battery power.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the information about the status of Wi-Fi.

android.permission.CHANGE_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to connect to and disconnect from Wi-Fi access points and to make changes to configured Wi-Fi networks.

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.MANAGE_DOCUMENTS.description: Allows an application to manage access to documents, usually as part of a document picker.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to the SD card.

android.permission.WRITE_SETTINGS.description: Allows an application to modify the system's settings data. Malicious applications can corrupt your system's configuration.

android.permission.CHANGE_CONFIGURATION.description: Allows an application to change the current configuration, such as the locale or overall font size.

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.description: Allows an application to read from SD Card.

android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO.description: Allows application to access the audio record path.

android.permission.CAMERA.description: Allows application to take pictures and videos with the camera. This allows the application to collect images that the camera is seeing at any time.

android.permission.VIBRATE.description: Allows the application to control the vibrator.

android.permission.GET_TASKS.description: Allows application to retrieve information about currently and recently running tasks. May allow malicious applications to discover private information about other applications.

android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

android.permission.READ_PROFILE.info: read the user's personal profile data
android.permission.READ_PROFILE.description: Allows an application to read the user's personal profile data.

android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE.description: Allows the application to access the phone features of the device. An application with this permission can determine the phone number and serial number of this phone, whether a call is active, the number that call is connected to and so on.

android.permission.CAPTURE_AUDIO_OUTPUT.description: Allows an application to capture audio output.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

android.permission.READ_LOGS.description: Allows an application to read from the system's various log files. This allows it to discover general information about what you are doing with the phone, potentially including personal or private information.

android.permission.MODIFY_AUDIO_SETTINGS.description: Allows application to modify global audio settings, such as volume and routing.

android.permission.SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW.description: Allows an application to show system-alert windows. Malicious applications can take over the entire screen of the phone.

android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE.description: Allows a regular application to use Service.startForeground

android.permission.REQUEST_INSTALL_PACKA.info: Allows an application to request installing packages.
android.permission.REQUEST_INSTALL_PACKA.description: Malicious applications can use this to try and trick users into installing additional malicious packages.

com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEI.description: Permission for cloud to device messaging.

"live_game_overall_desc_finshing_5" : "After killing the dolphins, you have the chance to win 150 times the super prize!"
"live_game_overall_desc_finshing_6" : "Every time the fish gets closer, you can catch 100 times the golden tiger shark!"
"live_game_overall_desc_finshing_7" : "After killing the electric eel, a lightning will hit a large number of small fish!"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_11" : "10.After choosing the fruits, you will need to choose between LEFT or RIGHT;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_12" : "11.Click LEFT or RIGHT to start the game, the bet will be the reward you just got;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_13" : "12.If you guess the result, the reward will be doubled and you can keep playing;"

"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_14" : "13.If you don't guess correct the LEFT or RIGHT game, the reward will be taken and you can't guess again LEFT or RIGHT. You only will be able to play again the fruit game;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_15" : "14.If you click other buttons while playing LEFT or RIGHT, you will lose the choice to guess, and you only will be able to play the fruit game;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_16" : "15.In AUTO mode, you will automatically play the LEFT or RIGHT game."
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_2" : "1.Click on the bet area below and bet on the fruit you think will win;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_2_2" : "1.The numbers shown above the fruits in the yellow area are the fruits odds and are fixed;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_2_3" : "2.The fruits odds are shown in the green area over the fruits and will be lighten. The numbers can be random;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_2_4" : "3.The fruits odds shown in the red area will appear randomly in 50 and 100 times;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_3" : "2.Click on ALL to bet 1 time on all the fruits;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_3_2" : "1.When you get ONCE MORE, the game will go left or right according to which ONCE MORE you got;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_3_3" : "2.Red ONCE MORE at the left: It will keep the bet of the 5 fruits on the left and will bet again;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_3_4" : "3.Blue ONCE MORE at the right: It will keep the bet of the 5 fruits on the right and will bet again;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_4" : "3.You can only bet 1-9 times on each fruits;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_6" : "5.Click AUTO and the automatic mode will start according to the current bet;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_7" : "6.When click START and the silver coins will be deducted;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_8" : "7.When you click START, you can't undo or bet again, you can bet to the next round after the result is shown;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_9" : "8.If the fruits shown are the same as the ones that you bet on, you will get the reward;"
"live_game_overall_desc_plane_1" : "The enemy planes are coming, to protect our homeland, hurry to fight!"
"live_game_overall_desc_plane_2" : "Shooting the planes needs buy bullets; if you shoot down the plane, you will get rewards;"
"live_game_overall_desc_plane_3" : "You can click + or - to switch bullets. The more expensive the bullet, the higher rewards you will get."
"live_game_overall_desc_plane_4" : "Tips: By pressing on the screen, it will continuously attack; If not hit the plane, silver coins won't be deducted."
"live_game_overall_desc_play_doung_1" : "Whack a Minion is a game that tests your reaction speed."
"live_game_overall_desc_play_doung_2" : "Use the hammer and whack the naughty minions that will appear from the icy caves. Whenever you whack one, you will have a chance to get silver coins!"

"live_game_overall_desc_play_doung_3" : "You need silver coins to use a hammer. Each time you whack, you spend 10/100/1,000/10,000 silver coins. If you hit the target, you can get a prize. You can use hammers with different prizes, the more expensive the hammer is, the higher the reward will be."

"live_game_overall_desc_play_doung_4" : "The Boss will appear regularly with a certain probability of being captured. Players who can capture the Boss will get 10% to 50% bonus in the Jackpot, and other players can get the remaining bonus in proportion to the consumption."

"live_game_sicbo_game_rule_3" : "2. Big, Odds:X 2, the total score will be from 11 to 17 (inclusive) with the exception of a triple"
"live_game_sicbo_game_rule_4" : "3. Any Tripl, Odds:X 30, any of the triples will appear"

"live_game_overall_desc_finshing_1" : "Súper Pesca es un juego recreacional que pone a prueba tus habilidades visuales y cerebrales."
"live_game_overall_desc_finshing_2" : "Pásalo súper agarrando todo tipo de peces que estan nadando. ¡Usa el arma para disparar cuántas burbujas puedas!"

"live_game_overall_desc_finshing_5" : "Después de matar a los delfines, ¡tienes la oportunidad de ganar 150 veces el súper premio!"
"live_game_overall_desc_finshing_6" : "¡Cada vez que el pez se acerca, puedes atrapar 100 veces el tiburón tigre dorado!"
"live_game_overall_desc_finshing_7" : "¡Después de matar la anguila eléctrica, un rayo le dará a una gran cantidad de peces pequeños!"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_10" : "9.Número de premios = Número de apuestas x Probabilidades"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_11" : "10.Después de elegir las frutas, necesitarás elegir entre izquierda left o derecha right;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_12" : "11.Haz clic en LEFT o RIGHT para empezar el juego, la apuesta será el premio que obtuviste;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_13" : "12.Si adivinas el resultado, el premio será doble y podrás seguir jugando;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_14" : "13.Si no adivinas correctamente el juego de left or right, el premio no se entregará y no podrás adivinar nuevamente en el juego left or right;"

"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_15" : "14.Si haces clic en los otros botones mientras estas jugando left or right, perderás la oportunidad de adivinar y sólo podrás jugar el juego de las frutas;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_16" : "15.En modo AUTO podrás jugar automáticamente el left or right"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_2" : "1.Haz clic en el área de apuestas y apueste en la fruta que pueda salir;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_2_2" : "1.Los números sobre las frutas en el área amarilla son las probabilidades de las frutas y son fijos;"

"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_2_4" : "3.Las probabilidades de las frutas en el área roja aparecerán aleatoriamente entre 50 y 100 veces;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_3" : "2.Haz clic en ALL para apostar 1 vez en todas las frutas;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_3_2" : "1.Cuando te toca ONCE MORE, el juego ira izquierda o derecha según el ONCE MORE que te haya tocado;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_3_3" : "2.El ONCE MORE rojo a la izquierda: Mantendrá la apuesta de las 5 frutas en la izquierda y se apostará de nuevo;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_3_4" : "3.El ONCE MORE azul a la izquierda: Mantendrá la apuesta de las 5 frutas en la izquierda y se apostará de nuevo;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_4" : "3.Sólo puedes apostar entre 1 a 9 veces en cada fruta;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_5" : "4.Haz clic en UNDO para eliminar todas las apuestas;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_6" : "5.Haz clic en AUTO y comenzara el modo automático según la apuesta actual;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_7" : "6.La monedas de plata se descontarán cuando hagas clic en START;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_8" : "7.Al hacer clic en START, ya no puedes deshacer o apostar nuevamente. Puedes apostar en la siguiente vuelta, después que se muestre el resultado;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_9" : "8.Si las frutas elegidas son las mismas que apostaste, obtendrás tu premio;"
"live_game_overall_desc_plane_1" : "¡Vienen los aviones enemigos, para proteger nuestra patria, apresúrate a luchar!"
"live_game_overall_desc_plane_2" : "Disparar a los aviones necesita comprar balas; si derribas el avión, obtendrás recompensas;"

"live_game_overall_desc_play_doung_3" : "Necesitas monedas de plata para poder usar el martillo. Cada vez que golpees uno, gastarás 10/100/1,000/10,000 monedas de plata. Si le das al blanco, puedes obtener un premio. Hay martillos con diferentes precios, mientras más caro es el martillo, mayor será la recompensa."

"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_14" : "13.如果玩家猜错了左右的结果，则系统收回奖金，同时失去参与猜左右环节的资格，回到猜水果环节中；"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_15" : "14.如果玩家在猜左右时点击了其他按钮，则视为放弃猜左右环节，回到猜水果环节中；"

"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_2" : "1.点击下方的押注区，便可下注哪个水果会赢；"

"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_2_3" : "2.绿色区的水果赔率将根据其上方亮着小灯的数字而随机变化；"

"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_3" : "2.点击ALL可对所有的水果下 1 注；"

"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_3_3" : "2.左边的红色ONCE MORE：将会保留押注区左边 5 个水果的押注状态而再玩一次；"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_3_4" : "3.右边的蓝色ONCE MORE：将会保留押注区右边 5 个水果的押注状态而再玩一次。"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_6" : "5.点击AUTO，则会根据当前的押注情况开始自动模式；"

"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_9" : "8.如果开出的水果与自己押注的水果相同，则可以获得奖金；"

"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_13" : "12.如果玩家猜中了左右的结果，則獎金翻被，並且還可以繼續參加；"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_14" : "13.如果玩家猜错了左右的结果，則系統收回獎金，同時失去參與左右競猜的資格，回到猜水果環節中；"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_15" : "14.如果玩家在猜左右時點擊了其他按鈕，則視為放棄猜左右環節，回到猜水果環節中；"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_16" : "15.在自動模式中，會自動跳過猜左右環節。"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_2" : "1.點擊下方的押注區，便可下注哪個水果會贏；"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_2_2" : "1.黃色區的水果賠率根據其上方的數字而固定；"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_2_3" : "2.綠色區的水果賠率將根據上方亮著小燈的數字而隨機變化"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_2_4" : "3.紅色區的水果賠率將在 50 倍和 100 倍中隨機出現一種"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_3" : "2.點擊ALL可對所有水果下 1 注；"

"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_3_3" : "2.左邊的紅色ONCE MORE：將會保留押注區左邊 5 個水果的押注狀態而再玩一次；"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_3_4" : "3.右邊的藍色ONCE MORE：將會保留押注區右邊的 5 個水果的押注狀態而再玩一次。"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_6" : "5.點擊AUTO，則會根據目前的押注情況開啟自動模式；"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_8" : "7.點擊START，則無法再撤銷呀注或者重新下注，只能等待本輪開獎結果公布後才能進行操作；"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_9" : "8.如果開出的水果與自己押注的水果相同，則可以獲得獎金；"
"live_game_overall_desc_plane_1" : "敵機突襲，為了自己的家園，趕緊來作戰吧！"

"live_game_overall_desc_plane_3" : "你可以點擊-或+來切換砲彈；砲彈價格越高，獲得的獎勵越豐富。"
"live_game_overall_desc_plane_4" : "小技巧：長按屏幕，砲彈會連續攻擊；若沒有擊中飛機，不會扣除遊戲幣。"
"live_game_overall_desc_play_doung_1" : "打豆豆是一款考驗反應速度的休閒遊戲"
"live_game_overall_desc_play_doung_2" : "調皮的小豆豆們會從冰凍中冒出來，使用槌子敲打它們，就有一定的機率擊中並且獲得銀幣獎勵喔！"
"live_game_overall_desc_play_doung_3" : "使用槌子需要花費銀幣，擊打 1 次豆豆，消耗10/100/1,000/10,000 個金幣，擊中目標可以獲得對等獎勵。你可以選擇不同價格的槌子，槌子越貴，擊中豆豆的獎勵越高"

"live_game_overall_desc_finshing_1" : "लकी फिशिंग एक मनोरंजक खेल है जो मस्तिष्क और दृश्य कौशल का परीक्षण करता है."
"live_game_overall_desc_finshing_2" : "गहरे समुद्र में सभी प्रकार की मछलियों को पकड़ने का मज़ा लें। हथियार उठाओ और जितना संभव हो उतने बुलबुले शूट करें!"
"live_game_overall_desc_finshing_3" : "मछली को शूट करने के लिए, आपको गोलियों को खरीदना होगा। मछली पर एक बार क्लिक करें जो आगे बढ़ रहा है और संबंधित इनाम प्राप्त करने के लिए इसे कैप्चर करें."
"live_game_overall_desc_finshing_4" : "आप इसे स्विच करने के लिए बुलेट के बगल में + या - पर क्लिक कर सकते हैं। बुलेट जितनी महंगी होगी, इनाम उतना ही अधिक होगा."
"live_game_overall_desc_finshing_5" : "डॉल्फ़िन को मारने के बाद, आपके पास 150 गुना सुपर पुरस्कार जीतने का मौका है!"
"live_game_overall_desc_finshing_6" : "हर बार जब मछली करीब आती है, आप गोल्डन टाइगर शार्क को 100 बार पकड़ सकते हैं!"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_11" : "10.फलों को चुनने के बाद, आपको LEFT या RIGHT में से चुनना होगा;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_12" : "11.गेम शुरू करने के लिए LEFT या RIGHT पर क्लिक करें, शर्त सिर्फ आपको मिला इनाम होगा;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_13" : "12.यदि आप परिणाम का अनुमान लगाते हैं, तो इनाम दोगुना हो जाएगा और आप खेलते रह सकते हैं;"

"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_14" : "13.यदि आप LEFT या RIGHT गेम को सही नहीं मानते हैं, तो इनाम लिया जाएगा और आप फिर से LEFT या RIGHT का अनुमान लगा सकते हैं। आप केवल फिर से फ्रूट गेम खेल पाएंगे;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_15" : "14.यदि आप LEFT या RIGHT खेलते समय अन्य बटन क्लिक करते हैं, तो आप अनुमान लगाने के लिए विकल्प खो देंगे, और आप केवल फलों का खेल खेल पाएंगे;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_16" : "15.ऑटो मोड में, आप स्वचालित रूप से बाएँ या दाएँ खेल खेलेंगे."
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_2" : "1.नीचे शर्त क्षेत्र पर क्लिक करें और उस फल पर दांव लगाएं जो आपको लगता है कि जीत जाएगा;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_2_2" : "1.पीले क्षेत्र में फलों के ऊपर दिखाई जाने वाली संख्याएँ फल की बाधाएँ हैं और इन्हें ठीक किया जाता है;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_2_3" : "2.फलों के अंतर को फलों के ऊपर हरे क्षेत्र में दिखाया गया है और हल्का किया जाएगा। संख्या यादृच्छिक हो सकती है;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_2_4" : "3.लाल क्षेत्र में दिखाए जाने वाले फल के आकार 50 और 100 बार में बेतरतीब ढंग से दिखाई देंगे;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_3" : "2.सभी फलों पर 1 बार दांव लगाने के लिए सभी पर क्लिक करें;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_3_2" : "1.जब आप ONCE MORE प्राप्त करते हैं, तो खेल आपके अनुसार ONCE MORE के अनुसार बाएं या दाएं जाएगा;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_3_3" : "2.जब आप ONCE MORE प्राप्त करते हैं, तो खेल आपके अनुसार ONCE MORE के अनुसार बाएं या दाएं जाएगा;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_3_4" : "3.ब्लू दाईं ओर अधिक: यह दाईं ओर 5 फलों की शर्त रखेगा और फिर से दांव लगाएगा;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_4" : "3.आप प्रत्येक फलों पर केवल 1-9 बार दांव लगा सकते हैं;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_5" : "4.सभी दांवों को साफ़ करने के लिए UNDO पर क्लिक करें;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_6" : "5.ऑटो पर क्लिक करें और स्वचालित मोड चालू शर्त के अनुसार शुरू होगा;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_7" : "6.ऑटो पर क्लिक करें और स्वचालित मोड चालू शर्त के अनुसार शुरू होगा;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_8" : "7.जब आप START पर क्लिक करते हैं, तो आप पूर्ववत या शर्त लगा सकते हैं, परिणाम दिखाए जाने के बाद आप अगले दौर में दांव लगा सकते हैं;"
"live_game_overall_desc_fruit_machine_9" : "8.यदि दिखाए गए फल वही हैं जो आप पर दांव लगाते हैं, तो आपको इनाम मिलेगा;"
"live_game_overall_desc_plane_1" : "जीतने की राशि = प्रतीक की बाधाओं * प्रतीक की शर्त राशि!"
"live_game_overall_desc_plane_2" : "विमानों की शूटिंग के लिए गोलियों को खरीदने की ज़रूरत है; यदि आप विमान को मारते हैं, तो आपको पुरस्कार मिलेगा;"
"live_game_overall_desc_plane_3" : "बुलेट स्विच करने के लिए आप + या - पर क्लिक कर सकते हैं। जितनी महंगी बुलेट होगी, उतने ही ऊंचे इनाम मिलेंगे."
"live_game_overall_desc_plane_4" : "टिप्स: स्क्रीन पर दबाकर, यह लगातार हमला करेगा; यदि विमान नहीं मारा, तो चांदी के सिक्के नहीं काटे जाएंगे."
"live_game_overall_desc_play_doung_1" : "Whack a Minion एक गेम है जो आपकी प्रतिक्रिया की गति का परीक्षण करता है."

"live_game_overall_desc_play_doung_2" : "हथौड़े का उपयोग करें और बर्फीले गुफाओं से दिखाई देने वाले शरारती टकसालों को मिटा दें। जब भी आप एक झटके में झटके मारेंगे, तो आपके पास चाँदी के सिक्के पाने का मौका होगा!"

"live_game_overall_desc_play_doung_3" : "एक हथौड़ा का उपयोग करने के लिए आपको चांदी के सिक्कों की आवश्यकता होती है। हर बार जब आप अजीब करते हैं, तो आप 10/100 / 1,000 / 10,000 चांदी के सिक्के खर्च करते हैं। यदि आप लक्ष्य को मारते हैं, तो आप पुरस्कार प्राप्त कर सकते हैं। आप विभिन्न पुरस्कारों के साथ हथौड़ों का उपयोग कर सकते हैं, हथौड़ा जितना महंगा होगा, उतना अधिक इनाम होगा."

"live_game_overall_desc_play_doung_4" : "बॉस पकड़े जाने की एक निश्चित संभावना के साथ नियमित रूप से दिखाई देगा। जो खिलाड़ी बॉस को पकड़ सकते हैं उन्हें जैकपॉट में 10% से 50% बोनस मिलेगा, और अन्य खिलाड़ियों को उपभोग के अनुपात में शेष बोनस मिल सकता है."

playstore_details.title: MICO Chat: Meet New People & Live Streaming
playstore_details.description:
If you are free and want to find someone to chat, MICO is your best choice. There are interesting live streams, full of surprises with random stranger chats, funny photos, and live chat. With real-time translation you can chat and date with strangers all over the world without any language barrier, you might meet your soulmate in MICO!

😍Tons of talented and beautiful broadcasters who come from United State have joined MICO, their attractive live shows will make you enjoyable. Download the app and interact with them. Join MICO USA.😍

High lights:
🔥Live streaming platform for everyone
🔥Meet and chat with strangers via random match
🔥The brand idea of “Play Together”, a worldwide live chat party
Live & Social Features:
Random Stranger Chat: Meet and chat with strangers via random match
-Pick a 100% match by swiping left or right, meet strangers accurately and fast. Randomly chat with strangers and Date real girls nearby or worldwide.
-Once you match someone, you will go to the chat room, then with messages, voice, and video you can chat with strangers and date them.

Live Streaming: Go live and watch live stream whenever you want
-Watch the live stream and enjoy live videos. Tons of talented broadcasters from more than 100 different countries are gathered in MICO. They offer thousands of exciting live shows every day. Filter live streams based on your interests or countries.
-1 touch to go live. Dancing, singing, talk show, online game, no matter what talent you have, MICO will be the biggest stage for you to broadcast your talents, everyone can be a star in MICO. New beautiful stickers and filters make you cuter, more beautiful and more confident in the live video.

Group Live Chat: Voice or live video chat with more people
-The more people watching, the more amazing the video chat will be. Join a group chat room and start a voice or live chat party with strangers, make friends and have fun with beautiful girls and handsome guys. 
-Create a multi-guest video chat room, invite more friends via video call to live chat with you or wait strangers enter to your live room, live chat or voice chat with them, meet more interesting people.

2v2 Video Live PK: New upgrade of traditional Live PK mode
-2v2 Live PK is not only the live stream competition between broadcasters but also with the audience. A broadcaster can invite a friend to start a 2v2 live PK, the loser will accept the lovely punishment. Come and enjoy a funny live PK.

World Travel: Meet fresh faces around the world
-MICO takes you to travel to every corner of the world to meet new people and chat with strangers, pick a popular city or match a random city to meet strangers.
-Use filter tags to find the people you share interest with to chat and meet.

Share moments: Enjoy the fun with friends or people nearby
-By sharing photos and short videos on moments you will catch strangers eyes around you and will increase your chances of dating and chatting with strangers nearby.

Real-time Translation: No barrier in stranger chat
-Click the translation button to easily break the language barrier in random stranger chat.
-Match random chat with strangers around the world without any language problem in MICO. It is easy to date or makes friends from other countries whenever and wherever you want.
 
Meet me in MICO, one of the most popular worldwide social networking apps where you can enjoy live streams, meet a soulmate, random chat with strangers, short videos & photos sharing, video live chat!
Your questions and feedback are always welcome! Please drop us a line:

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/micoteam
